\id LUK - Djinang 
\h Luke 
\toc1 Luke 
\toc2 Luke 
\toc3 LUK 
\mt1 Luke  
\c 2  
\s1 Christmas Story  
\p
\v 6 A bilakiṉiŋ biliŋ ŋuḻi bil nyininyipm, waḻirr inga yulguŋiliban Merigi miri gurrulk inga buŋtjigi.  
\v 7 Girri nyanŋaŋ miḻimiṯi djawal-giŋiniban, a Meridji marrŋili ŋunukima, girri garrpiniban mirikaldji giḻiwiḻiŋir, girri yakirr-galwupiṉi ŋunyili djapiḏili yurryarrkiṉiŋili nyaliŋiri buluki mala djin ḏirradjigi yurryarr ŋuli bulukiŋirar bala’mirri. Bilapilaŋirgi nyani yakirr-galwupiṉi djapiḏili bulukiŋiraŋ, gima wirr gadjigarr biliŋki ṉambiḏi bala’mirri yulpilŋiraŋ, gima ŋunuŋ bala’ŋurrum rarri inydji barŋiliban.   
\p
\v 8 Manymak, ŋidjirrkŋ Bitiliyim gurrbiwi, gar-gurryili murrurrtmirri nyibi maypal-djamagiṉpili djani djin nyininy kiriny, maypal bimbi mala djiny djin djagadjny kirinyban, a ŋunupan ŋurrum gar-maliridjiniban.  
\v 9 Girri ŋunukiṉiŋban wurpmi Garrayaŋ djamagiṉiŋ wugiḻi nyani djina birraldjini, a Garrayar warrdjinirnir djiny ḻiwḻiwmiyŋili, a munutjaban warrpaḏaḏadjini ŋidjirrkŋ djanŋar biṯma maṉŋibirri. Wanaban inga djin ŋuy-yawŋiniban.  
\v 10 Bil ŋunukima wugiḻi djina waŋini, djina binjin, ‘Iŋkiban ildji yawŋidji. Butjir inydji ildji kuwi, ŋarri ildjarr birruŋiliban djaŋuny buṯal, marrga bukmak yulpili wanaban djin ṉitjanydjidji ŋunukiṉiŋ djiniŋ djaŋuny djin marrŋirrdji.  
\v 11  Gima djini’djiniŋ maliri, nyani Wanŋirnyakiṉiŋ ildja buŋtjiliban ŋildjaŋi, djiḻi gurrbiwi Dabidaŋ nyani Garray djawal-nyaŋiṉiban ŋunukima Godaŋ Yirryirrpinirbi yul.  
\v 12 A bilapilaŋ djiniŋ warŋarri djaŋunygiṉiŋ djarri kirimban ŋildjiki, marrga ildji birraldjnyirdjigi ŋunuŋ yidjipili: ildji manyaŋi nyaninyi mirikaldji garrpini, a ŋurri kirim djapiḏimirri bulukiŋirar.’ Bilapilaŋ ŋunuŋ wugiḻ djina bindjini maypal-djagadjnyakiṉpilŋirgi.   